N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 22.10 - Reports

State Regulations

Superintendents of schools and county boards of elections
shall forward to the commissioner within 30 days after election day a
statistical report on a form furnished by the commissioner, and shall retain
all other literacy testing materials for a period of one
year. Notes
